title: Dead Man's Cell Phone Continues AU Theatre Season (Ashland University)
text: ( Source : Ashland University ) 10/22/15 ASHLAND, Ohio - Ashland University Department of Theatre continues its 2015-2016 season with Sarah Ruhl 's wildly imaginative comedy ' Dead Man 's Cell Phone .' Directed by guest artist Rachael Swartz,
